{"tid":1450190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:35:36.000Z","uid":301841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5d346a539b09a73756ff25be7ae0d9e80a7c1e","tid":1450190,"uid":301841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:23:54.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=9e9024de\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=45abc993\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"4ad8f149ad30f448e610baf63a3ace019f92213b","tid":1450190,"uid":301841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"自推X1"},{"pid":"fe7da594591409c124a07deb74355f07ab3d747e","tid":1450190,"uid":301841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"自推X2"},{"pid":"33a1f8c1768bccc5fbff30be734ec9611cf7bb89","tid":1450190,"uid":301841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"自推X3"},{"pid":"0afea892c68adf49c2c2e468b52fd60e51ab2b29","tid":1450190,"uid":301841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"自推X4"},{"pid":"e6